      "updated": 1777053583937,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cost -> Using LLM once or twice is fine but if we are making tool or building tool on top of that\n    then again and again calling LLM model and so many services like this, ultimately it is going\n    to cost us.\n    \n    So to avoid this when we can just use some basic ML algorithm we will try to use ML over there.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cost -> Using LLM once or twice is fine but if we are making tool or building tool on top of that\n    then again and again calling LLM model and so many services like this, ultimately it is going\n    to cost us.\n    \n    So to avoid this when we can just use some basic ML algorithm we will try to use ML over there.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
