      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Script and Automate\nand now machine will\nwill do this automatically\n\nfor example cron is running at every night at 9 PM\nthat is a part of automation, Now machine is doing itself,\nHuman is not required, that is also comes under\ndomain of AI",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
