    {
      "id": "lsVN0QflqdCAJTXQrbAEz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 988.904908128105,
      "y": 52104.46809582592,
      "width": 1133,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bal",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1801932051,
      "version": 643,
      "versionNonce": 923160851,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777862902404,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In this learning we dont have nothing like input , output. Either we have nothing or we have half or\nwe have whole. we are not concerned about this. Reinforcement learning is more about, it will make some\nprediction and it will always ask for a Yes or No. And based on yes or no model will keep on training\nitself. So model starts almost with scratch with zero and over the period of time, it learns, based on\nwhatever feedback we are giving.\nSo someday if AI kills us or take our job or something like that, It is our own reinforcement. AI did \nnothing.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In this learning we dont have nothing like input , output. Either we have nothing or we have half or\nwe have whole. we are not concerned about this. Reinforcement learning is more about, it will make some\nprediction and it will always ask for a Yes or No. And based on yes or no model will keep on training\nitself. So model starts almost with scratch with zero and over the period of time, it learns, based on\nwhatever feedback we are giving.\nSo someday if AI kills us or take our job or something like that, It is our own reinforcement. AI did \nnothing.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aRfgNBKh5GY5aLM5hKnAG",
