      "updated": 1777863277327,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "where we have a graph in x and y, and wherein line is going and we have to predict where this line will go next\nthese kind of models are generally regression based model. So here we are trying to find a pattern\nor f(x) for this line. these models are regression model.\n  ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "where we have a graph in x and y, and wherein line is going and we have to predict where this line will go next\nthese kind of models are generally regression based model. So here we are trying to find a pattern\nor f(x) for this line. these models are regression model.\n  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
